comment_data.body:
This was fixed with release 47 of the plugin.

The problem here is that the plugin 46 was installed from the JetBrains plugin repository and that version did not support the beta of Android Studio. Installing it from the dev channel would have worked. In any case, the stable version of 47 works with both beta and canary builds of Android Studio. At least until the next API change in the canary.
